rows.label: tev060401_MSG0001
rows.name:
That green smoke friends call kridokan air and sell for
big money?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0002
rows.name: It can only be obtained in caves of Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Chiroro saw it, but never bothered bottling since it
just looked like green fart or something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0004
rows.name:
But Chiroro was wrong! So wrong!
Think of fortune Chiroro could have made...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0006
rows.name: Lot of Nopon have VERY similar problem.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0007
rows.name:
Stress of running from Prone and adapting to life in
new place causes fur to fall out big time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0008
rows.name:
But Nopon need worry no more! Chiroro come up
with legendary puffy-hair supercream to make
embarrassing problem go away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0009
rows.name:
True, ingredients are tough to come by,
and many Nopon too shy to purchase...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060401_MSG0010
rows.name:
But Felice say Chiroro need to run more ethical
business, so Chiroro putting customer needs above
personal gain![ST:wait ]
